summary: It\'s Legen... wait for it... dary! Legendary!!
descriptionHtml:
Kids, I\'m going to tell you an incredible story, the story of how I met your mother. It all started the day I was sent to Helgen to be killed, that\'s a funny story that I\'ll get to later...                (Insert story here).

  This is a save game of a character named Ted Mosby, who has similar looks to that of Ted Mosby from the popular TV show How I met your Mother. Obviously the looks are not exact, yet with the limitations of Skyrim it\'s not possible to be exact. He was originally just a random character I made, then one of my friends pointed out the similarities of my character to Ted. So I renamed him Ted and made this save for others to enjoy :)

  Ted is a level 1 Imperial that starts out at the only place you\'d see him, a bar! Or in this case an Inn. He starts inside The Sleeping Giant Inn in Riverwood.

  Now go out and find the one!

  Note: To be able to use him as he looks in the pictures you\'ll need a few mods...
*Better males - Beautiful nudes and faces New hairstyles  http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2488 by Chris57
*ApachiiSkyHair (For this particular hair style you need to download the male hairs v1.0) http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/10168 by apachii 
*The Eyes Of Beauty http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/13722 by LogRaam
author: Gabe
